Public timing summary for FP_MUL 0.5 ns target
==============================================

This is a sanitized timing summary. The private report contained
library-specific cell names, delay/load values, operating corners, and a full
critical path through the mapped standard-cell netlist. Those details were
removed for public release.

Target clock period : 0.5 ns
Timing slack        : +2 ps
Cost group          : CLK
Start point         : shift_amt_reg_reg[1]/CP
End point           : rounded_mantissa_reg_reg[41]/D

The full private timing path is intentionally not included because it exposes
confidential standard-cell library and process-characterization details.
